00:08:58.780 --> 00:08:59.980
It's my fault.

00:09:00.220 --> 00:09:01.820
From today on,

00:09:02.300 --> 00:09:03.859
I will never cross the line again.

00:09:03.860 --> 00:09:04.459
If...

00:09:04.460 --> 00:09:05.260
Yan.

00:09:10.020 --> 00:09:12.460
If there's even the slightest chance,

00:09:13.460 --> 00:09:15.980
I will never let her go so easily.

00:09:19.462 --> 00:09:20.582
